result.name: 潤發飯店

reviews.text: An old store frequented by locals. Ordered chicken mushroom rice pot (北菇滑鸡饭). Considering the large portion HK$29 was a bargain. Decent place for a quick and affordable meal. But given the location, don't expect a squeeky clean dining environment with English speaking staff.
New renovations and now is Shanghai fusion style
價錢適中，有中式菜同上海菜，出品都算尚可，最重要是食材新鮮
本地自制點心，新鲜出品，地方簡潔
價格合理的老店，地點方便。
